      "title": "Emergency passed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "As the new government's first proposal in Parliament, the motion to extend the emergency law for another month was passed today (27) by a majority vote.",
        "120 votes were cast in favor of the motion and 63 against. Accordingly the motion was carried by 57 additional votes."
